6 March 2017The Governance &amp; Administration Cluster chaired by Adv Ngoako Ramatlhodi, Minister for the Public Service and Administration will brief media on the implementation of the Cluster programme of action for the year, following the 2017 State of the Nation Address.The briefing will also outline progress that has been made and future plans to achieve the National Development Plan Vision 2030.Members of the media are invited as follows:Date: Thursday, 9 March 2017 Venue: Imbizo Media Centre, Ground Floor, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape Town Time: 09h00 NB: There will be a video link up to GCIS Pretoria, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard Street, PretoriaNB: Kindly confirm attendance by e-mail to:Andile Duka (Cape Town) E-mail: Andiled@gcis.gov.za Cell: 071 154 5619Takalani Mukwevho (Pretoria) E-mail: takalanim@gcis.gov.za Cell: 082 227 9308Enquiries:Dumisani Nkwamba Cell: 082 885 9448Issued by Government Communication and Information System